Computing Surveys
The Association for Computing Machinery (AC) publishes Computing
Surveys, comprehensive readable surveys and tutorial programs.  
The surveys give guided tours through the literature and explain
topics to those who seek to learn the basics of areas outside
their specialties.  Computing Surveys' carefully planned and
presented introductions are also an excellent way for professionals
to develop prospective and identify trends in complex technologies.
